# Workspace hygiene
.DS_Store
._*
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# Generated analysis/build/test artifacts
_reports/*
tests/e2e/node_modules/
# Whitelist tracked QA evidence for the module-template-v4 slice program
# (Slice 1 dispatch board, Slice 2 nonconformance, future Wave 1 slices).
# Reviewed off-line by external evaluators; required to be visible on GitHub.
!_reports/module-template-v4/
# Whitelist the 12-week deploy playbook prompt scaffolds (committed by
# a6a5fa65 as feature content for the AI authoring flow). Without this
# exception the deploy CI's repo-boundary check blocks every push.
!_reports/deploy-playbook/
# Whitelist the KPI upgrade prompt pack — a sequential AI execution plan
# (10 stages) the user points an AI session at. Tracked so it survives a
# fresh clone and is available to any AI session.
!_reports/kpi-upgrade-prompts/
# Whitelist the practical KPI upgrade prompt pack v2, which supersedes and
# expands the KPI CNC execution prompts while remaining a tracked AI artifact.
!_reports/kpi-upgrade-prompts-v2/
# Whitelist KPI audit/report outputs so AI sessions can commit evidence
# produced during the KPI upgrade program (prompt pack 01→09).
!_reports/kpi/
# Whitelist UoM V3 No-Guess World-Class hardening reports (P00..P13). Each
# V3 prompt emits an evidence-locked report set under this path; the
# Controlled Source Boundary check must let them ride to GitHub for the
# external integration readiness review.
!_reports/uom-measurement-conversion-v3/
# Whitelist V1 UoM planning reports — referenced by the V3 contradiction
# ledger and external evaluators per the same precedent as v3.
!_reports/uom-measurement-conversion-v1/
# Whitelist MDA Sequential Authority prompt-pack audit bundle (governance
# artifacts committed by 23b7f35ff for external evaluator review on GitHub).
!_reports/agent-audits/
# Whitelist orders-v3 Module Master v3-G14..G25c slice audit evidence
# (live-test findings, backend persistence proof, CSS token wiring audit).
# Tracked so external evaluators and future AI sessions can review the
# audit trail from the v3 property dock hardening sprint.
!_reports/module-master-properties-dock/
# Whitelist RACI v3 authority consolidation audit bundle — sequential
# governance evidence set reviewed by external evaluators.
!_reports/raci-v3/
# Whitelist the Graphics Authority adversarial critique + Lego-SSOT redesign
# proposal — strategy deliverables reviewed alongside the dark-mode fix.
!_reports/graphics-authority-critique/
